node.text: Although you might know them as Swiss cheese plants and split-leaf Philodendrons, #Monstera plants aren't really Philodendrons (or Swiss cheese). This week, Eileen walks through tips for caring for Monstera and how to help them thrive.

node.title: Monstera Care with Eileen  Indoor House Plants

node.text: Becoming a master indoor gardener just got a little easier. We’re launching a new series on #houseplant care with help from our Garden Center expert, Eileen. Check out her favorite 7 easy indoor plants at youtube.com/homedepot, and you’ll be well on your way to your own indoor jungle.
